# kiwi-ng

> KIWI NG is an OS image and appliance builder
> More information: https://osinside.github.io/kiwi/

- Build an appliance:

`kiwi-ng system build --description={directory value} --target-dir={directory value}`

- Show build result of built appliance:

`kiwi-ng result list --target-dir={directory value}`

- Display help:

`kiwi-ng help`

- Display version:

`kiwi-ng -v`
